Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前  有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底两万哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌懦弱的人  无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在作梦之前  我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的音乐盒开启  发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你眼前  有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't  forget  to  try  in  mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时值西元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号告别后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强、娜蒂亚与大王\N搭乘飞机来到岛屿上空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却突然遭到不名人士攻击\N而迫降于森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强他们在那里认识了\N住在岛上的小女孩,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉的双亲\N已遭神秘组织杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰迪丝三人组\N也被那个组织抓了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强他们虽然也遭到攻击\N但总算是逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.24,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔天早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强与娜蒂亚\N将玛莉双亲的死讯告诉了她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但玛莉却不懂那所代表的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人也下定决心\N要保护这名小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#06  孤岛要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉的家旁边\N有一间很大的教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这一带吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个星期天我都会跟爸爸妈妈\N一起去祈祷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗,玛莉真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂的位置大致吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人型战车在拉着车?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,是车子在操纵人型战车吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亚特兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亚特兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩们尚未出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子要留活口,知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好,回去你的岗位\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩们?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是在找我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子要留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的应该是娜蒂亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是港口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方在上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条就是玛莉说的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港口?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对,有很多船停靠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从教堂旁边的路直直走\N就能看到很多船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸常带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戒备还真森严
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本溜不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人的货物量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这里的电量也好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴黎也没亮成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从哪里输送来的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着山里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山里会有什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-晚安之吻\N-吻?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不晓得吗?\N妈妈都会亲我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好睡吧,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈都是说"晚安,玛莉"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论村里还是港口\N全都是那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是向人求助…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上哪找人帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们全都是杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有没被他们发现\N躲了起来的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就跟那些人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你告诉我那些人在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.06,0:07:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛,就会胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我怎么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该要想个更…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是在夫妻吵架吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-才不是呢\N-才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉,对不起\N不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧的,你别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,靠我们两个\N根本逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上还有个玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让玛莉遇上危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地的中心应该就在\N岛屿中央的露天矿坑里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.47,0:08:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上我会再去查探情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以跑出去\N会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的花园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以,强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入对方基地太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想被抓住的人\N应该都被关在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对这座岛的认识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有问玛莉而画出来的\N这张地图而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须潜入基地\N取得更多情报才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经想好潜进去\N也不会被发现的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不去冒这个险\N是无法离开这座岛屿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄色的,白色的,红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为牧克做一条\N天堂最美的项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你摘吧,小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-玛莉…\N-别去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在去了\N大家都会被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正在等\N看有没有人会去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奸诈的一群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没有其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,全员准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-走吧,娜蒂亚\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉,你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会去救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到烟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密基地应该就在那下头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉与大王就在那里是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把他们救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是利用以前的坑道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好亮的灯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么时候发明的?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我跟鹦鹉螺号借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条输电线路\N应该会通到他们的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据玛莉所说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有间大发电厂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这里头有许多电罗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个带有相当强大的电压
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便乱碰会被烧成焦炭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出口吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到他们的大本营了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小心点\N-嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是岛上的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是湖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是秘密基地?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八成是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是火力发电厂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多烟囱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中央的塔会是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来又不像天线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发着光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是座玻璃塔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么用途呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一头的那个是城堡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,这地方还真惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密密麻麻都是管子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么的工厂呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,你什么都不晓得吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得再到下面去调查才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是输送带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要输送什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干不下去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛兰迪丝小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,那边的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么\N还不快点干活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别在那边唠唠叨叨的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己过来挖如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然逼我这种\N娇弱的少女做苦工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为男人你知不知羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还挺行的嘛\N让我刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快进入\N20世纪的科学时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种苦工实在跟不上潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西先借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就快点开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你们那么讨厌工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就带你们去个好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要邀请我们参加晚餐会吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以,会场就在地下监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你们举办\N不吃不喝的盛大派对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把人带下去\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是淑女耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对我客气点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢蛋,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这条输送带停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让它停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从这种地方下去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走在上头会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要沿着这些管子\N到城堡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会弄得浑身都是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊,又不是来野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也对,这是为了玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死我了\N怎么突然就动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那只海中怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然是潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它将我爸爸的船…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人走出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亚特兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是什么人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地位似乎很高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亚特兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您的大驾,石像鬼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那名女孩捉到了吗?\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经掌握人质\N很快就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论使出怎样的手段都无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一定要活捉她\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织规模似乎相当庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新亚特兰?\N会是什么意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熔矿炉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜…娜蒂亚,下面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃到下面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去会粉身碎骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住我,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造山铜调整得如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预定迟了0.01%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是来得及在实验前完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到外头马上会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但万一要是掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会连渣都不剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.81,0:19:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样吓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是将石英熔化\N做成玻璃砖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要做什么用呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只会想那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当现代化的自动工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头没半个工人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却有看守的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来该怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜里看守的人应该会少一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时再…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时再躲到那边的输送带下面\N慢慢前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照以上所言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人造山铜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃集合我们目前所有科学力量\N所得到的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就理论上而言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它应该能展现\N如同预料之中的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光有理论只是纸上谈兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须实际用得上才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得\N这还是第一次这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前并未出现类似情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是在对什么东西产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚的"蔚蓝之水"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点,往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,光芒消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不停下来就要开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧,只是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经被团团包围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高举双手乖乖出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.26,0:22:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像可以通到其它地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去之后\N你就拿着这个逃到那个洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只数到五
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.42,0:22:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我出去,你就趁机…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙要抓的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.66,0:22:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.70,0:23:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,我一定会回来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那名女孩,要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追,别让她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.70,0:23:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-从右方包抄\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.22,0:23:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待续)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.96,0:24:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.17,0:24:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喃喃自语  仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.45,0:24:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try  安慰的话语\N是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.59,0:24:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.37,0:24:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.67,0:24:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.34,0:24:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使跌倒或感到迷惘\N仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜蒂亚,我一点都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.87,0:25:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.47,0:25:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强…强一定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.27,0:25:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.58,0:25:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石像鬼为什么会称呼我为公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.05,0:25:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底两万哩  下一回\N“巴别塔”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.82,0:25:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看喔
